```.vindrc
# vim-like navigation

nmap <ctrl-i> <to_insert>
vmap <ctrl-i> <to_insert>
" Press Ctrl-I to enter insert mode without clicking.

nmap <ctrl-'> <to_resident>
imap <ctrl-'> <to_resident>
rmap <ctrl-'> <to_insert>
" Allow using icapslock to switch between resident and insert  

gvmap v <to_gui_normal>
evmap v <to_edi_normal>

gvmap <ctrl-m> <gridmove>
gvmap Fh <easyclick>
gvmap a <click_right>
gvmap o <click_left>


```